â€¢	Limitations/Problems 

-	No unique ID in the dataset.
-	High cardinality of categorical variables increased the dimensionality of the data 
-	High variance in the dataset as it is not particularly for residential real estate, therefore huge outliers in terms of land size.
- Can be complemented with data on market dynamics








